│ updates dominance information correctly when   │
│ modifying the IR. This may involve changes to  │
│ how `ScalarToTreeEntries` and                  │
│ `ValueToGatherNodes` are updated during        │
│ instruction reordering.\n\n5. **Conclusion**:  │
